# Build context for the `ai` service is ./apps. It only needs apps/ai + apps/scraper
# (the editable path dep). Exclude the heavy, constantly-changing web app and caches,
# otherwise BuildKit's context walk fails with "walker is closed: context canceled".
web/
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.fastembed_cache/
**/.env
